data.description: Stylish light filled home with the primary bedroom downstairs. An additional two more bedrooms, bath and flex/office space downstairs. Upstairs is a large loft, bedroom, full bath and an additional generous closet. This well thought out floor plan has water views from the lovely pond it sits on. New carpet in the bedrooms. New microwave. The dishwasher, refrigerator and garbage disposal were replaced in 2021. Ship lap was added to the master in 2022. Upgraded light fixtures in the dining room, foyers and kitchen. Linnen Place is a small enclave of homes located less than one mile from Jennie Moore Elementary and Laing Middle School. Linnen Place is located just off Hamlin Rd between Hwy 17 and Rifle Range Rd. The IOP Connector is just 3 miles to the south.
